data.description: Beautiful one story 3 bedrooms and 3 baths in the amazing Sunterra Master-Planned community. The home is spacious with an open concept great for entertaining and family interaction. The kitchen is gorgeous with white 42" cabinets, luxury granite countertops and island, and stainless steel farmhouse single bowl sink. This home boasts bright natural lighting throughout. Each bedroom is spacious and has 3 bathrooms to accommodate a family and guests. Wood-like Tile Floors flow seamlessly throughout the entryway, kitchen, dining area, family room, hallways, utility room, and all the baths, providing a cohesive and easy-to-maintain living space. The spacious primary suite is a sanctuary of relaxation. It features a HUGE walk-in closet, 36"-High Cabinets with Separate Sinks, and a Garden Tub. Don't miss this opportunity to experience the resort lifestyle and make this stunning 1-story, 3-bedroom, 3-bath home yours today. Contact us to schedule a viewing fort this exceptional property!
